The paper discusses the backpropagation algorithm, which is a fundamental technique in neural networks, making cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) the most likely category. The paper also discusses the use of neural networks to solve differential equations, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG and cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of activation functions, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and signal processing (cs.SI).
